5:["$","section",null,{"className":"bg-blue-50 py-14","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-anton text-3xl uppercase mb-6 text-text-main text-center","children":["Local Roads and Driving Conditions in ","Arana Hills"]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 mb-10 text-center mx-auto","children":[["$","p","0",{"children":"Looking for driving lessons in Arana Hills? UNO Driving School provides calm, automatic driving lessons for learners across Arana Hills, Ferny Hills, Keperra and Everton Hills. Our 5-star instructors help Arana Hills students pass their Queensland driving test on the first attempt."}],["$","p","1",{"children":"Arana Hills sits at the junction of the Brisbane City and Moreton Bay region corridors. The suburb is built across steep, undulating topography, resulting in a winding, complex residential road network. For an early learner, this terrain forces rapid development of steering finesse, constant speed modulation, and a confidence of hill starts."}],["$","p","2",{"children":"At the base of the hills, the Arana Hills Kmart Plaza and Patricks Road create a busy commercial artery. Our instructors utilise this structure to build student confidence methodically—mastering the quiet, steep neighborhood loops before transitioning downward into the intense pedestrian and car-park environments of the shopping precinct, preparing them thoroughly for testing at Strathpine or Toowong."}],["$","p","3",{"children":"Arana Hills learners test at the Strathpine or Toowong TMR Customer Service Centres. Free pickup from Arana Hills, modern automatic vehicles, Afterpay available. Book today."}]]}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4","children":[["$","li","0",{"className":"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-blue-100 flex items-start gap-4","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-primary text-xl mt-0.5","children":"📍"